 BY FOLASHADE KEHINDE FORMER Minister of Women Affairs, Aisha Jummai Al-Hassan, aka Mama Taraba, is dead. She was said to have died on Friday, in Cairo, Egypt, at the age of 61. Al-Hassan, on July 27, 2018, resigned as the Minister of Women Affairs, to contest the governorship election in Taraba. No official statement had been released by the family as of the time of filing this report. Details shortlyâ€¦ 